---
// Página principal de SENZA - Sistema de Generación de Hidrógeno para Automóviles
---

<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<meta name="description" content="SENZA - Revoluciona tu automóvil con tecnología de hidrógeno. Ahorra hasta 20% de combustible y reduce emisiones en más del 50%." />
		<title>Multi Novelty's LLC - SENZA Hydrogen Technology | Power From Water</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body class="bg-senza-primary text-senza-accent font-sans overflow-x-hidden">
		<!-- Header -->
		<header class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-senza-primary/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-senza-border shadow-sm">
			<nav class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 py-6 flex items-center justify-between">
				<div class="flex items-center">
					<div class="w-28 h-14">
						<img src="/logo.svg" alt="Multi Novelty's LLC Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-12">
					<a href="#producto" class="text-senza-gray hover:text-senza-accent transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Producto</a>
					<a href="#tecnologia" class="text-senza-gray hover:text-senza-accent transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Tecnología</a>
					<a href="#beneficios" class="text-senza-gray hover:text-senza-accent transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Beneficios</a>
					<a href="#contacto" class="text-senza-gray hover:text-senza-accent transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Contacto</a>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
					<a href="/en" class="text-senza-gray hover:text-senza-accent transition-colors text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
						<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129"/>
						</svg>
						EN
					</a>
					<a href="/comprar" class="bg-senza-blue text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-senza-dark-blue transition-all text-sm shadow-lg">
						Comprar
					</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<!-- Hero Section with Video -->
		<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
			<!-- Video Background -->
			<div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full">
				<video 
					class="w-full h-full object-cover" 
					autoplay 
					muted 
					loop 
					playsinline
					poster="/images/foto-real-kit.jpg"
				>
					<source src="/video/presentacion.mp4" type="video/mp4">
					Tu navegador no soporta videos HTML5.
				</video>
				<!-- Video overlay for better text readability -->
				<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Floating elements over video -->
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
				<div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-senza-blue to-senza-light-blue rounded-full animate-float"></div>
				<div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-senza-light-blue to-senza-blue rounded-full animate-float" style="animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
				<div class="absolute top-1/2 right-10 w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-senza-dark-blue to-senza-blue rounded-full animate-float" style="animation-delay: -4s;"></div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Content overlay -->
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center relative z-10">
				<div class="animate-slide-up">
					<div class="mb-8">
						<div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm border border-senza-border rounded-full mb-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-senza-blue to-senza-light-blue rounded-full mr-4 animate-pulse"></div>
							<span class="text-senza-gray text-sm font-medium flex items-center">
								<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
								</svg>
								Tecnología Verde Revolucionaria
							</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Enhanced title with glow effect -->
					<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-light mb-8 text-white leading-tight relative drop-shadow-lg">
						<span class="relative">
							<span class="font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-green-300 via-senza-light-blue to-green-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent relative drop-shadow-xl">
								Ahorra y Cuida
								<!-- Glow effect -->
								<span class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-senza-light-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent blur-sm opacity-50">Ahorra y Cuida</span>
							</span>
							<br>
							<span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl">el Planeta</span>
						</span>
					</h1>
					
					<!-- Enhanced subtitle -->
					<p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
						<strong class="text-green-300">Reduce 70% las emisiones de CO₂</strong> mientras <strong class="text-senza-light-blue">ahorras entre 20% y 25% en combustible</strong>. 
						<span class="font-semibold text-senza-light-blue">SENZA</span> convierte tu vehículo en una herramienta de cambio ambiental.
					</p>
					
					<!-- Enhanced buttons with icons -->
					<!-- Stock Limited Notice -->
					<div class="mt-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-red-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-orange-400/30 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.732-.833-2.5 0L4.268 15.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"/>
							</svg>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-300">Stock Limitado</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-white/90 text-center mb-4">
							<strong>Producto de lanzamiento con disponibilidad limitada.</strong><br>
							Tiempo de entrega: hasta 30 días hábiles.
						</p>
						<div class="flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-orange-200">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
							</svg>
							Reserva tu unidad ahora
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center mt-8">
						<a href="/comprar" class="group bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:from-green-600 hover:to-blue-600 transition-all shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:scale-105 flex items-center space-x-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Ahorrar y Cuidar el Planeta</span>
						</a>
						<button class="group border-2 border-white text-white bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-green-600 transition-all flex items-center space-x-2">
							<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
							</svg>
							<span>Ver Impacto Ambiental</span>
						</button>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Stats section -->
					<div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
						<div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/20 to-green-600/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4 border border-green-400/30">
							<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-300 mb-2">20% - 25%</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-white/90 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"/>
								</svg>
								Ahorro de Combustible
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-blue-600/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4 border border-blue-400/30">
							<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-300 mb-2">-70%</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-white/90 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
								</svg>
								Reducción CO₂
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/20 to-emerald-600/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-4 border border-emerald-400/30">
							<div class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-300 mb-2">0</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-white/90 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
								</svg>
								Emisiones Tóxicas
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Video controls overlay -->
			<div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-20">
				<button id="videoToggle" class="bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white p-3 rounded-full hover:bg-white/30 transition-all">
					<svg id="playIcon" class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
					</svg>
					<svg id="pauseIcon" class="w-6 h-6 hidden" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path d="M6 19h4V5H6v14zm8-14v14h4V5h-4z"/>
					</svg>
				</button>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Scroll indicator -->
			<div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
				<div class="w-6 h-10 border-2 border-white rounded-full flex justify-center">
					<div class="w-1 h-3 bg-white rounded-full mt-2 animate-pulse"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Product Section -->
		<section id="producto" class="py-24 bg-senza-secondary">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-20">
					<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light mb-6 text-senza-accent">
						Tecnología <span class="font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-senza-blue to-senza-light-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent">Avanzada</span>
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-senza-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						El sistema SENZA genera hidrógeno de alta pureza a partir de agua, revolucionando la eficiencia de tu automóvil.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
					<div class="space-y-10">
						<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-senza-border">
							<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">H</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-senza-accent">Tecnología PEM</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-senza-gray leading-relaxed">
								Membrana de intercambio de protones de última generación que garantiza hidrógeno 99.99% puro.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-senza-border">
							<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-light-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">C</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-senza-accent">Microcomputadora Inteligente</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-senza-gray leading-relaxed">
								Chip de 7nm que optimiza el rendimiento del motor en tiempo real según tus patrones de conducción.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-senza-border">
							<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-dark-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">I</span>
								</div>
								<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-senza-accent">Instalación No Invasiva</h3>
							</div>
							<p class="text-senza-gray leading-relaxed">
								Compatible con la mayoría de vehículos sin modificaciones al sistema original.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-2xl border border-senza-border">
						<div class="text-center mb-8">
							<img src="/images/foto-real-kit.jpg" alt="Kit SENZA Real - Fotografía del Producto" class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
						</div>
						<h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-senza-accent mb-8 text-center">Kit Completo SENZA</h4>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
							<div class="text-center p-4 bg-senza-secondary rounded-xl">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-blue rounded-xl mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">H</span>
								</div>
								<span class="text-sm font-medium text-senza-gray">Generador</span>
							</div>
							<div class="text-center p-4 bg-senza-secondary rounded-xl">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-light-blue rounded-xl mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">C</span>
								</div>
								<span class="text-sm font-medium text-senza-gray">Computadora</span>
							</div>
							<div class="text-center p-4 bg-senza-secondary rounded-xl">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-dark-blue rounded-xl mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">T</span>
								</div>
								<span class="text-sm font-medium text-senza-gray">Transformador</span>
							</div>
							<div class="text-center p-4 bg-senza-secondary rounded-xl">
								<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-senza-blue rounded-xl mx-auto mb-3 flex items-center justify-center">
									<span class="text-white font-bold">W</span>
								</div>
								<span class="text-sm font-medium text-senza-gray">Tanque</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Product Components Gallery -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-senza-secondary">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light mb-6 text-senza-accent">
						<span class="font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-senza-light-blue to-senza-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent">
							Componentes del Kit
						</span>
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-senza-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						Descubre cada pieza que conforma el sistema SENZA de generación de hidrógeno
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="space-y-8">
						<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-senza-border">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-senza-accent mb-4">Generador de Hidrógeno</h3>
							<p class="text-senza-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
								El corazón del sistema. Utiliza tecnología PEM para convertir agua en hidrógeno de alta pureza (99.99%) de manera eficiente y segura.
							</p>
							<div class="w-full">
								<img src="/images/pieza-individual-generador-hidrogeno.jpg" alt="Generador de Hidrógeno SENZA" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="space-y-8">
						<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-senza-border">
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-senza-accent mb-4">Microcomputadora Inteligente</h3>
							<p class="text-senza-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
								Chip de 7 nanómetros fabricado en Estados Unidos que optimiza automáticamente el rendimiento del motor según tus hábitos de conducción.
							</p>
							<div class="w-full">
								<img src="/images/pieza-individual-microcomputador.png" alt="Microcomputadora SENZA" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-16 text-center">
					<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-senza-border max-w-4xl mx-auto">
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-senza-accent mb-6">Kit Completo SENZA</h3>
						<p class="text-senza-gray mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
							Todo lo que necesitas para revolucionar tu automóvil en un solo paquete
						</p>
						<div class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto">
							<img src="/images/kit-completo.webp" alt="Kit Completo SENZA" class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-senza-accent/30">
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Real Kit Section -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-senza-secondary">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
						<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-senza-blue to-senza-light-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent">
							Kit Real en Funcionamiento
						</span>
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-senza-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						Fotografía real del kit SENZA tomada en nuestras instalaciones. Un producto tangible y funcional que puedes tener en tus manos.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-senza-border">
					<div class="text-center">
						<img src="/images/foto-real-kit.jpg" alt="Kit SENZA Real - Fotografía Original" class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-senza-accent/20">
					</div>
					
					<div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-senza-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
								<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-senza-accent mb-2">Producto Real</h3>
							<p class="text-senza-gray">Kit físico disponible para entrega inmediata</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-senza-light-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
								<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-senza-accent mb-2">Listo para Instalar</h3>
							<p class="text-senza-gray">Componentes probados y funcionando correctamente</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="text-center">
